      "note_no": "15",
      "note": "Lit., \"come forward with a surah like it, and call upon your witnesses other than God\" - namely, \"to attest that your hypothetical literary effort could be deemed equal to any part of the Qur'an.\" This challenge occurs in two other places as well (10:38 and 11:13, in which latter case the unbelievers are called upon to produce ten chapters of comparable merit); see also 17:88."
